# Naming conventions

Layout: [`addon-layering.mdc`](addon-layering.mdc) · Style: [`code-style.mdc`](code-style.mdc)

## Files: stem + suffix

| Suffix | Contains |
| --- | --- |
| `*.types.ts` | Types only |
| `*.constants.ts` | Named constants and env-backed literals — no functions |
| `*.utils.ts` | Pure helpers |
| `*.factory.ts` | Pure mappers (no I/O) |
| `*.handler.ts` | HTTP/SDK entry |
| `*.services.ts` | Outbound network I/O |
| `*.db.ts` | Persistence |

**This repo:** camelCase stems under **`src/`**.

## Functions and constants

- Name for the **dominant effect** — see [`function-operation-naming.mdc`](function-operation-naming.mdc)
- **`SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE`** for shared semantic constants
- Types only in **`*.types.ts`**
